These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
6 different games are played: canasta, bridge, domino, monopoly, backgammon, poker
The people have 6 different hobbies: woodworking, magic-tricks, puzzles, gardening, singing, card-games
 1. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
 2. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 3. the person playing backgammon is not the person who's hobby is singing##6
 4. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person playing bridge##6
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person playing monopoly##7
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person playing canasta##1
14. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
15. the person playing poker is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Game   | monopoly   | canasta | domino   | poker     | bridge    | backgammon   |
| Hobby           | singing | woodworking   | card-games | gardening | puzzles | magic-tricks |

