.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There 6 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, kiwi, nectarine, asparagus, kale
There are 6 different favourite colors: aquamarine, brown, blue, azure, orange, amber
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 2. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
 4. the person who likes brown is not the person eating nectarine##6
 5. the person eating carrot is not the person who likes aquamarine##6
 6. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
 8. the person eating asparagus is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
 9. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
10. the person who likes orange is somewhere between the person eating asparagus and the person eating eggplant##7
11. the person who likes amber is in an odd position##4
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
13. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
14. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Food   | asparagus        | nectarine | kale    | carrot    | kiwi | eggplant |
| Color      | brown | orange  | amber | azure | aquamarine | blue      |

