 3. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is not the owner of the rabbit##6
 6. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the goat and the owner of the rabbit##7
 7. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the goat##7
 8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the snake##7
10. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
12. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
13. the person who likes azure is the owner of the snake##1
14. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
