.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: begonia, zinnia, bellflower, daisy, orchid, daffodil
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, whist, canasta, bridge, snooker
 1. the person playing whist is the person who growsbellflower##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
 5. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
 6. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who growsorchid and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 7. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 9. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
10. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
11. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
12. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person who growsbellflower and the person playing billiard##7
13. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Flower         | zinnia   | orchid | begonia      | daisy | daffodil  | bellflower   |
| Game   | canasta | snooker  | billiard | mah-jongg   | bridge | whist |

