.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
There are 6 different nationalities: indian, german, argentine, turkish, chinese, spanish
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, water, fanta, 7up, tea
 1. the chinese is on the left or right of the spanish##3
 2. the argentine is on the left of the turkish##1
 3. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 4. the indian is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking sprite##7
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 6. the argentine is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
 9. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
13. the german is somewhere between the indian and the argentine##7
14. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the chinese##1
15. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Nationality   | argentine         | turkish | german | indian   | spanish | chinese  |
| Beverage     | 7up | fanta  | water  | tea | sprite  | coffee |

 